SUMMARY:OV Pickleball Open Play (120m)
DESCRIPTION:Room: OV Pickle East 1\, 2\; OV Pickle West 1\, 2\nLocatio
 n: Ocotillo Village\nPickleball is available at Ocotillo Village.  Ev
 ery Tuesday and Thursday each week from 1:00PM to 3:00PM and every Su
 nday 10am to 1pm on the Weekends.  \n\n4 Courts are available for all
  player levels who want to have a fun\, socialize and recreational pl
 ay.\n\nCertified Pickleball Coach\, James Cole will be providing Coac
 hing and Instruction for those who are needing or wanting some extra 
 instruction or 1 on 1 Coaching.\n\nThe Basketball Court will not be o
 pen for for Basketball play until after the Scheduled Pickleball Open
  Play Times are over.\n\nPlay time is reserved for the first 20 that 
 register on the Village Mobile App.  Registration opens 48 hours prio
 r to the day and time of the next scheduled Pickleball Open Play.   R
 ules and Play Policy will be posted at the Court.\n\n*There will be n
 o Officials. Honesty and Good Sportsmanship will be expected at all t
 imes.
END:VEVENT
