SUMMARY:$The Nervous System Reset: From Stress to Regulation (180m) - 
 Ericka
DESCRIPTION:Instructor: Ericka Brian\nRoom: OV Mind/Body Studio\nLocat
 ion: Ocotillo Village\nThe Nervous System Reset: From Stress to Regul
 ation\nSunday\, April 12 | 2:30 pm-3:30 pm\n\nIn today’s high-perfo
 rmance culture\, chronic stress has become normalized. Join Ericka an
 d Michael through an incredible workshop of Tai Chi and meditation. T
 his workshop teaches members how to regulate their nervous system usi
 ng breathwork\, somatic awareness\, and intentional movement. Partici
 pants will learn the science behind sympathetic vs. parasympathetic a
 ctivation and leave with practical tools to reduce anxiety\, improve 
 sleep\, and increase emotional resilience.\n \n$35 member | $45 non-m
 ember\n\nEricka Brian | ebrian@dmbclubs.com\n \nNo shows and cancelat
 ions within 36 hours will be charged the event fee.
END:VEVENT
